---
title: Chicken, Bacon & Veggie-Loaded Filo Pie with Sesame Seeds
description: This cosy dinner packs in both loaded veggies, bacon and chicken that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a light and flakey filo pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ab503bce6b1bd057254e03-45b75c4b.jpeg
